-- Facebook and Groupon Will Continue to Grow, Milner Tells CNBC
-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 2012-01-27T13:56:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-27/facebook-and-groupon-will-continue-to-grow-milner-tells-cnbc.html
Companies like Facebook Inc. and
 Groupon Inc (GRPN) . will continue to grow, said Russian billionaire
Yuri Milner, whose investments include both companies.  Milner doesn’t think there is a “bubble” in valuations of
internet technology companies and added that he has been “only
buying so far.” He spoke in an interview with CNBC television
in Davos,  Switzerland , today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
